{"tid":378762,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"大地魚湯底雲吞麵簡直天堂","createTime":"2017-08-28T17:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T04:17:23.000Z","uid":14730,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f13d87a87f998647919638cd7e02b640cddf06d","tid":378762,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:18:45.000Z","msg":"現在的雲吞麵店，收你十幾蚊碗麵，敢說湯底都是用豉油、味精整色整水調出來，吃完滿嘴乾涸；半分大地魚香也嚐不出來。<br />\n<br />\n要做出一碗傳統正宗的雲吞麵，根本不可能沒有大地魚的份兒。湯骨十斤、蝦殼八斤、大地魚兩斤、金華火腿半斤、羅漢果兩個，花十五小時用文火慢熬，熬出十桶清澈甘甜的湯底。<br />\n<br />\n「大地魚好重要，湯底甘不甘鮮，全靠它一力吊出味來？」所以，選上好的大地魚乾絕對不能馬虎，不然轉頭便壞了一鍋湯。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2xrSGmI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2xrSGmI&d=TGuA74kbfzTUufBc9i%2FkiDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=c1e721f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2xrSGmI</a>"},{"pid":"c29be53ce9d9f15849f2d9ca0ce7cca81f28e30c","tid":378762,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:33:54.000Z","msg":"牛腩撈+雲吞"},{"pid":"7515fbdfb4ebf626b8cd3e71f7ad6913ced0b731","tid":378762,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:40:15.000Z","msg":"好鍾意佢個湯底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3456d5661b342ff5acd71473e5502260d39567","tid":378762,"uid":55419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T17:42:20.000Z","msg":"有冇十幾蚊咁平"},{"pid":"53c746e30b3a225390d655c9c2a4f1dfa7c83ef3","tid":378762,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:19:40.000Z","msg":"邊道重有正宗雲吞麵？麥文記？"},{"pid":"90725505fc80a8e25e507628c4d576ba4bb5e87a","tid":378762,"uid":15880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T18:29:08.000Z","msg":"香港地食麵仲有湯底架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1b8e05a2384ba7c