slike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T19:23:50.000Z","msg":"本身憎食雲吞麵 亦都唔明點解啲人鍾意食<br />\n應該我食開個啲係好參次<br />\n俾佢講到好吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54edb0167bf83a17db100b1c56e50c69752ebad","tid":378762,"uid":77755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T00:46:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但片入面間野名不見經傳wor...掂唔掂呀</blockquote><br />\n出名先未必好野喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e9581e91c7722a8d03abb990bed9fbcfa662da","tid":378762,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T01:09:49.000Z","msg":"深仔記中規中矩，未到話最好個班"},{"pid":"44a1ffaf13d371f7746f7a3561891397e2442b47","tid":378762,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T01:17:16.000Z","msg":"買樽大地魚粉, 好平"},{"pid":"156ad2dfe7f1bd6e8819d2d9a997554d45eb94d1","tid":378762,"uid":130349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T04:17:23.000Z","msg":"深水埗 旺角都正"}]}